    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-10-16T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-10-16T00:00:00-05:00" n="599" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d599">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Terrell</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Olney</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Constantinople</hi> (<hi rend="smallcaps">Pera</hi>)</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-10-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 16,
                                1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>At Akhissar fifty Armenians killed 9tli instant. Massacre Trebi-zond last
                            week; over five hundred killed. Hunter and Chilton, now there, telegraph
                            safe. Situation here still precarious. British fleet is still at
                            Lemno.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Terrell.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
